data.description: Spacious ranch home located on a quite cul de sac on the edge of Carey.  This home had a large kitchen and half bath added on by previous owners, allowing a nice size dining room area open to the living room. The attached garage was also transformed into a fourth bedroom. There's a detached two car garage along with a shed that will stay.  Wonderful opportunity for those seeking a single story home!
